Goals
-------
HARD
Every role assigned to an actor
Incompatible roles cannot be assigned to the same actor
An actor can't have one of their prohibited roles

SOFT
Every actor should have approximately the same number of lines
An actor should not be assigned to one of their discouraged roles (?)

LINE NUMBERS:
